description: A brain aneurysm survivor, Siike also worked at Arcana & Platinum Studios as a writer, and more recently in marketing at Top Cow. He's written articles for Bleeding Cool, and Hollywood Reporter, and has been a guest on Dan Harmon's podcast Harmontown and Conversations w/ Matt Dwyer. He was also co-host of the hit podcast, Nerd Nation. Currently he is Editor and Chief and Marketing Director at OSSM Comics.
name: Siike Donnelly
